gar: A Novel Novice&nbsp;Feature</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-10847"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/bitter-language-by-elka-cloke-a-novel-novice-feature/"><i>Bitter Language</i> by Elka Cloke: A Novel Novice&nbsp;Feature</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-19332"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/city-of-fallen-angels-not-so-mundane-moments/"><i>City of Fallen Angels</i>: Not So Mundane&nbsp;Moments!</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-24478"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/dark-eden-by-patrick-carman-a-novel-novice-featured-book/"><i>Dark Eden</i> by Patrick Carman: A Novel Novice Featured&nbsp;Book</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-36085"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/deadly-delicious-by-k-l-kincy/"><i>Deadly Delicious</i> by K.L.&nbsp;Kincy</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-26291"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/ditched-by-robin-mellom-a-novel-novice-featured-book/"><i>Ditched</i> by Robin Mellom: A Novel Novice Featured&nbsp;Book</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-15734"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/escape-from-furnace-series-by-alexander-gordon-smith/"><i>Escape from Furnace</i> Series by Alexander Gordon&nbsp;Smith</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-11324"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/i-now-pronounce-you-someone-else-by-erin-mccahan/"><i>I Now Pronounce You Someone Else</i> by Erin&nbsp;McCahan</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-13785"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/matched-by-ally-condie-a-novel-novice-feature/"><i>Matched</i> by Ally Condie: A Novel Novice&nbsp;Feature</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-23940"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/silence-by-becca-fitzpatrick-a-novel-novice-feature/"><i>Silence</i> by Becca Fitzpatrick: A Novel Novice&nbsp;Feature</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-