s/torment-by-lauren-kate-a-novel-novice-feature/"><i>Torment</i> by Lauren Kate: A Novel Novice&nbsp;Feature</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-17654"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/water-for-elephants-by-sara-gruen-a-novel-novice-feature/"><i>Water for Elephants</i> by Sara Gruen: A Novel Novice&nbsp;Feature</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-19172"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/where-things-come-back-by-john-corey-whaley/"><I>Where Things Come Back</i> by John Corey&nbsp;Whaley</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-13214"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/wildwing-by-emily-whitman-a-novel-novice-feature/"><i>Wildwing</i> by Emily Whitman: A Novel Novice&nbsp;Feature</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-9954"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/zombies-vs-unicorns-which-team-are-you-on/"><i>Zombies vs. Unicorns</i>: Which team are you&nbsp;on?</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-22697"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/countdown-to-sprinkles-secrets-by-lisa-schroeder/">Countdown to <i>Sprinkles &amp; Secrets</i> by Lisa&nbsp;Schroeder</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-22716"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/countdown-to-swear-a-swoon-novel-by-nina-malkin/">Countdown to <i>Swear</i> (a <i>Swoon</i> Novel) by Nina&nbsp;Malkin</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-22701"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-author-lisa-mcmann-the-unwanteds/">Featured Author: Lisa McMann &amp; <i>The&nbsp;Unwanteds</i></a></li><li class="page_item page-item-19806"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-blood-red-road-by-moira-young/">Featured Book: <i>Blood Red Road</i> by Moira&nbsp;Young</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-16415"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-clarity-by-kim-harrington/">Featured Book: <i>Clarity</i> by Kim&nbsp;Harrington</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-12833"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-coming-of-the-dragon-by-rebecca-barnhouse/">Featured Book: <i>Coming of the&nbsp;Dragon</i></a></li><li class="page_item page-item-24637"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-darker-still-by-leanna-renee-hieber/">Featured Book: <i>Darker Still</i> by Leanna Renee&nbsp;Hieber</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-30779"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-fingerprints-of-you-by-kristen-paige-madonia/">Featured Book: <i>Fingerprints of You</i> by Kristen-Paige&nbsp;Madonia</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-22694"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-fury-by-elizabeth-miles/">Featured Book: <i>Fury</i> by Elizabeth&nbsp;Miles</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-22711"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-goliath-by-scott-westerfeld/">Featured Book: <i>Goliath</i> by Scott&nbsp;Westerfeld</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-13109"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-revolution-by-jennifer-donnelly/">Featured Book: <i>Revolution</i> by Jennifer&nbsp;Donnelly</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-22098"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-sleight-by-jennifer-sommersby/">Featured Book: <i>Sleight</i> by Jennifer&nbsp;Sommersby</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-27757"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-take-a-bow-by-elizabeth-eulberg/">Featured Book: <i>Take a Bow</i> by Elizabeth&nbsp;Eulberg</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-24466"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-the-chronicles-of-harris-burdick/">Featured Book: <i>The Chronicles of Harris&nbsp;Burdick</i></a></li><li class="page_item page-item-21228"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-the-day-before-by-lisa-schroeder/">Featured Book: <i>The Day Before</i> by Lisa&nbsp;Schroeder</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-25058"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-the-pledge-by-kimberly-derting/">Featured Book: <i>The Pledge</i> by Kimberly&nbsp;Derting</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-30795"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-vessel-by-sarah-beth-durst/">Featured Book: <i>Vessel</i> by Sarah Beth&nbsp;Durst</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-24218"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/featured-book-virtuosity-by-jessica-martinez/">Featured Book: <i>Virtuosity</i> by Jessica&nbsp;Martinez</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-35776"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/holiday-baking-week-lisa-schroeders-its-raining-cupcakes-series/">Holiday Baking Week: Lisa Schroeder&#8217;s <i>It&#8217;s Raining Cupcakes</i>&nbsp;Series</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-18722"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/featured-books/the-official-blog-tour-for-a-need-so-beautiful-by-suzanne-young/">The Official Blog Tour for <i>A Need So&nbsp;Beautiful</i></a></li></ul></li><li class="page_item page-item-35763"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/lists/">Lists &amp; Features</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-213"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/features/videos/">Videos</a></li></ul></li><li class="page_item page-item-6 page_item_has_children"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/classroom-tools/">Classroom</a><ul class='children'><li class="page_item page-item-22981"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/classroom-tools/classroom-ideas/">Classroom Ideas</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-194"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/classroom-tools/essay-project-topics/">Essay &amp; Project&nbsp;Topics</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-192 page_item_has_children"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/classroom-tools/lesson-plans/">Lesson Plans &amp; Study&nbsp;Guides</a><ul class='children'><li class="page_item page-item-675"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/classroom-tools/lesson-plans/a-christmas-carol-activities-and-educational-links/">A Christmas Carol &#8211; Activities and Educational&nbsp;Links</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-632"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/classroom-tools/lesson-plans/a-christmas-carol-lesson-ideas-and-activities/">A Christmas Carol &#8211; Lesson Ideas and&nbsp;Activities</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-651"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/classroom-tools/lesson-plans/night-lesson-plan-and-activities/">Night Lesson Plan and&nbsp;Activities</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-671"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/classroom-tools/lesson-plans/the-outsiders-activities-and-educational-links/">The Outsiders &#8211; Activities and Educational&nbsp;Links</a></li></ul></li></ul></li><li class="page_item page-item-32"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/resources/">Tools</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-2 page_item_has_children"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/about/">About</a><ul class='children'><li class="page_item page-item-172"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/about/contact-us/">Contact Us</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-178"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/about/staff/">Meet the Novel Novice&nbsp;Staff</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-176"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/about/mission-statement/">Mission Statement</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-790"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/about/news-media/">News &amp; Media</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-22882"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/about/novel-novice-contest-policy/">Novel Novice Contest&nbsp;Policy</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-22889"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/about/novel-novice-book-review-policy/">Novel Novice: Book Review&nbsp;Policy</a></li><li class="page_item page-item-241"><a href="http://novelnovice.com/about/our-network/">Our Network</a></li><li class